<td><strong>Keywords</strong></td>
<td>Low volume, high value, technical</td>
<td>High volume, broad, emotional</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>Buying cycle</strong></td>
<td>3-12 months, multiple stakeholders</td>
<td>Minutes to days, individual</td>
</tr>
<tr>
