<h2>FAQ</h2>
<p><strong>What is B2B SEO?</strong></p>
<p>B2B SEO is search engine optimization for businesses that sell to other businesses. It focuses on low-volume, high-value keywords that attract decision makers during a 3-12 month buying cycle. Organic search generates 44.6% of all B2B revenue, making it the single most valuable marketing channel for B2B companies.</p>
<p><strong>How is B2B SEO different from B2C SEO?</strong></p>
<p>B2B SEO targets technical, problem-focused keywords with lower search volume but higher deal values ($10K-$500K+). B2C targets broad, emotional keywords with high volume. B2B content serves a 6-10 person buying committee across months. B2C content drives individual purchases in minutes.</p>
<p><strong>How long does B2B SEO take to show results?</strong></p>
<p>Most B2B SEO campaigns show measurable results in 6-12 months. B2B SaaS companies reach breakeven in approximately 7 months. Content published in month 1 continues generating leads in month 12 and beyond. SEO ROI accelerates as your content library and domain authority grow.</p>
<p><strong>What content should B2B companies publish for SEO?</strong></p>
<p>Start with bottom-of-funnel content: competitor comparisons, pricing pages, and case studies. Then build middle-funnel content: buyer guides and tool comparisons. Finally, scale top-of-funnel educational content. Companies publishing 16+ blog posts per month generate 4.5x more leads.</p>
<p><strong>What is a good ROI for B2B SEO?</strong></p>
<p>The median B2B SEO ROI is 748%. B2B SaaS companies see 702% ROI with a 7-month breakeven period. A "good" ROI depends on your deal size and sales cycle, but anything above 300% after 12 months indicates a healthy program. Real estate, medical devices, and financial services see the highest returns.</p>
<p><strong>How much should a B2B company spend on SEO?</strong></p>
<p>B2B SMBs typically invest $2,000-10,000 per month on SEO (content, tools, and team time). Enterprise B2B companies invest $10,000-50,000+ monthly. Stacc offers 30 SEO articles per month at $99/mo, making consistent publishing accessible for B2B companies at any budget.</p>
<p>B2B SEO is a pipeline generation engine. Every article, comparison page, and case study creates a new entry point for qualified buyers to find your business. The companies that invest in consistent, expert-level content today will own the organic search results their competitors fight over tomorrow.</p>
